{"comments":"Dimension — Bounded positive integer atom for tensor dimensions.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nTensor dimensions are **strictly positive integers**. A dimension of 0\nor negative is meaningless and should be unrepresentable.\n\nThis module provides:\n- `Dim`: A positive integer dimension (minimum 1)\n- `DimVar`: A symbolic dimension for dynamic/unknown sizes\n- Operations that preserve positivity\n\n## Diffusion Model Context\n\nCommon dimension patterns:\n- Batch size: typically 1-128 (bounded by memory)\n- Sequence length: 77 (CLIP), 512, 1024, 2048, 4096\n- Embedding dim: 320, 640, 768, 1024, 1280, 2048\n- Channels: 3 (RGB), 4 (RGBA/latent), 64, 128, 256, 512, 1024\n- Spatial: 8, 16, 32, 64, 128, 256, 512, 1024 (powers of 2)\n\n## Invariants\n\n- All dimensions are >= 1\n- Symbolic dimensions (DimVar) are placeholders resolved at runtime\n- Dimension arithmetic preserves positivity where possible\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Prelude (Eq, Ord, Show, Semiring)\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[123,22],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Tensor/Dimension.purs","start":[123,13]},"title":"Dim"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Tensor","Dimension"],"Dim"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[125,32],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Tensor/Dimension.purs","start":[125,1]},"title":"eqDim"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Tensor","Dimension"],"Dim"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[126,34],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Tensor/Dimension.purs","start":[126,1]},"title":"ordDim"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Tensor","Dimension"],"Dim"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[129,24],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Tensor/Dimension.purs","start":[128,1]},"title":"showDim"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Semiring"],"Semiring"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Tensor","Dimension"],"Dim"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[135,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Tensor/Dimension.purs","start":[131,1]},"title":"semiringDim"}],"comments":"A concrete tensor dimension.\n\nAlways positive (>= 1). Constructed via `dim` which clamps to minimum 1.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[123,22],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Tensor/Dimension.purs","start":[123,1]},"title":"Dim"},{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[141,31],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Tensor/Dimension.purs","start":[141,16]},"title":"DimVar"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Tensor","Dimension"],"DimVar"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[143,38],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/